---
const pageTitle = "You're In! Check Your Email";
const pageDescription =
  "You're in! Check your email for your free guide and see the next simple step to start building online income.";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>{pageTitle}</title>
    <meta name="description" content={pageDescription} />

    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background: #0b1020;
        color: #fff;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: auto;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      h1, h2 {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      p {
        color: #cbd5e1;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .badge {
        display: inline-block;
        background: #1f2937;
        padding: 8px 14px;
        border-radius: 20px;
        font-size: 14px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      .box {
        background: #111827;
        padding: 25px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }

      .cta-btn {
        background: #facc15;
        color: #000;
        padding: 15px 20px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        font-weight: bold;
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 20px;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .steps {
        text-align: left;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }

      .steps li {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      footer {
        margin-top: 60px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #94a3b8;
      }

      .note {
        font-size: 14px;
        margin-top: 15px;
        color: #cbd5e1;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="container">

      <!-- CONFIRMATION -->
      <div class="badge">Step 1 Completed</div>

      <h1>You're In! Check Your Email</h1>

      <p>
        Your free guide is on its way. Please check your inbox (and spam folder if needed)
        to download it and get started.
      </p>

      <!-- NEXT STEPS -->
      <div class="box">
        <h2>Important: Do This Next</h2>

        <ul class="steps">
          <li>Open the email we just sent you</li>
          <li>Download your free guide</li>
          <li>Read the first few pages to understand the system</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- TRANSITION -->
      <div class="box">
        <h2>Want to Take the First Step Faster?</h2>

        <p>
          Inside the guide, you'll learn that every online income system needs traffic.
          Without traffic, nothing works.
        </p>

        <p>
          If you want a simple place to start, there is one platform many beginners use
          to get initial traffic without overcomplicating things.
        </p>

        <!-- CTA DAILYADS -->
        <a href="YOUR_DAILYADS_AFFILIATE_LINK" class="cta-btn">
          Explore a Simple Traffic Source
        </a>

        <!-- NUEVA FRASE (CLAVE) -->
        <p class="note">
           If you decide to join, just send me a message and I’ll personally help you get started 
        </p>

      </div>

      <!-- EXPECTATION -->
      <div class="box">
        <h2>What Happens Next?</h2>

        <p>
          Over the next few days, I’ll send you a few simple emails to help you understand
          how to build your first online income system step by step.
        </p>

        <p>
          Keep an eye on your inbox — that’s where the real value is.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- FOOTER -->
      <footer>
        This page is for educational and informational purposes only. Results are not guaranteed and will vary based on effort, consistency, skill, and market factors.
      </footer>

    </div>
  </body>
</html>